```cs
[SerializeReference, ReferencePicker] private List<IActionBase> actions = new List<IActionBase>();
```

I noticed that the RederencePicker does not work when LinkSelectable inherits from Selectable. But it *does* work if I make it inherit from MonoBehaviour. Is there a way for me to get it to work when inheriting from Selectable?

